<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,391,1304,1330]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="495">Pinnaspis strachani</emphasis>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Cooley" box="[406,567,1304,1330]" pageId="5" pageNumber="495" refString="Cooley, R. A. (1898) New species of Chionaspis and notes on previously known species. Canadian Entomologist, 30, 85 - 90. https: // doi. org / 10.4039 / Ent 3085 - 4" type="journal article" year="1898">Cooley, 1898</bibRefCitation>
